{"tid":158195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[炒哂車]【被屈賣核食品】無印良品反擊央視：公司地址當「產地」","createTime":"2017-03-16T06:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T12:28:38.000Z","uid":2110,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8652d64fea12088811accf8e885ef902dd22c5","tid":158195,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170316/56435212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170316%2F56435212&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=0e398c14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170316%2F56435212&h=bb5b5947\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170316/56435212</a><br />\n央視昨日於315世界消費者日晚上播出特備節目「315晚會」，踢爆消費陷阱。其中無印良品被指售賣來自日本核污染區的食品，當中包括無咖啡因香茅薏仁茶和雞蛋圓鬆餅。<br />\n<br />\n今日，無印良品公司發出聲明反擊，稱公司未進口及銷售任何中國政府明令禁止的日本核污染影響區域的食品，反指央視將當公司地址當成食品「產地」。<br />\n聲明全文如下：<br />\n1)此次引起誤解的原因是本公司所銷售的進口食品日文標識上所標示的「販賣者 株式會社良品計畫RD01東京都豐島區東池袋4-26-3」，而該信息為本公司母公司名稱及其法定註冊地址，並非本司所售進口食品的產地。<br />\n2)3&middot;15晚會所曝光的兩款進口食品的原產地如下：<br />\n無印良品無咖啡因香茅薏仁茶(谷物飲料) 原產地：日本福井縣<br />\n無印良品雞蛋圓鬆餅(熱加工糕點) 原產地：日本大阪府<br />\n3)本公司向全國消費者聲明，本公司進口及銷售的來自於日本國的食品，均嚴格遵守2011年4月8日國家質量監督檢驗檢疫總局(總局2011年第44號公告)《關於進一步加強從日本進口食品農產品檢驗檢疫監管的公告》及2011年6月13日國家質量監督檢驗檢疫總局頒布的國質檢食函【2011】411號《關於調整日本輸華食品農產品檢驗檢疫措施的通知》的規定，未進口及銷售任何中國政府明令禁止的日本核污染影響區域的食品。本公司進口及銷售的進口食品均有【原產地證明書】，且證明書正本已提交上海出入境檢驗檢疫局，並取得【中華人民共和國入境貨物檢驗檢疫證明】。每批次進口食品的報關報檢單證齊全合規。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489643165_57cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489643165_57cb.jpg&h=01a88af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489643231_b470.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489643231_b470.png&h=ab5d7b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489643236_3334.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489643236_3334.png&h=54643b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170316/large/1489643238_759d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170316%2Flarge%2F1489643238_759d.png&h=d34d4d14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9af6d304108c11789a91f1a10d388f0e75180c1a","tid":158195,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8977feee95586b0ec009e2217ad1fcf94fdb8b18","tid":158195,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾央視"},{"pid":"4b4d16f6a3682c7574150e6c492dc7abeea6da10","tid":158195,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ea327d4e042ee67df285362ead9dfd71761723","tid":158195,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:30:09.000Z","msg":"一係你央視唔得，一係你檢疫廢嘅<br />\n揀一樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80377fb0bf3a3d96d3b5fd00f5c2bd9d9b0e9ac3","tid":158195,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係你央視唔得，一係你檢疫廢嘅<br />\n揀一樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> why not both"},{"pid":"27be5edbd034fddc557c9a5f9f23113157a6c0d0","tid":158195,"u